com.orchestranetworks.ui.selection

Interface EntitySelection

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssociationEntitySelection, AssociationRecordEntitySelection, AssociationTableEntitySelection, DatasetEntitySelection, DataspaceEntitySelection, HierarchyEntitySelection, HierarchyNodeEntitySelection, RecordEntitySelection, TableEntitySelection, TableViewEntitySelection

    public interface EntitySelection
    Provides information on the current selection.

    This interface should not be implemented directly. Instead implement DataspaceEntitySelection, DatasetEntitySelection, TableViewEntitySelection, RecordEntitySelection, HierarchyEntitySelection, HierarchyNodeEntitySelection, AssociationEntitySelection or AssociationRecordEntitySelection.

    Since:
    5.8.0
